{
  "stem": "6944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And also because of the example in-- in Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the news went, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Flares.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would go with these flares at night-- and in Berrenrath, there were no lights in the street at that time-- and sing their German songs, the Horst Wessell song, which became their anthem. 'Deutschland, Deutschland,' of course. 'Deutschland, Deutschland Uber Alles' was their anthem.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this became the Nazi song, Horst Wessell song, because I believe he was a martyr early in the-- in the-- in their struggle.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they passed our house, we closed the shutters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We looked through the shutters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was eerie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was frightening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole thing had changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't understand what had happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then in June-- in June, all of a sudden, very late at night-- it must have been like 11 o'clock at night-- there was a knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you get, of course, very frightened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother opened the door, and there was a lady standing there, who was a customer of hers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she was the wife of a official from the-- from the-- from the factory there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a great official.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she came to tell-- warn my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, my husband has just returned from a meeting in town, in-- in this village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said the meeting was very rowdy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somebody got up and says, there is a Jew living in this town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this Jew has-- is sucking our blood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Look, he has got two houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One house is not enough for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They're sucking our blood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, that wasn't good for the Nazis because, of course, the Jews are sucking our blood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews are our misfortunes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That became a slogan.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
